        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段再挫 日股暫跌逾千點 韓股跌超過3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">布蘭特期油稍早前升越每桶109美元，繼續影響亞洲股市氣氛。日韓股市今早初段均再挫。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241203_FI_source-ap_Japan_Financial_Markets_-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241203_FI_source-ap_Japan_Financial_Markets_-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時08分，日經平均指數跌1054點或2.03%，報50831點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫時跌164點或3.12%，報5112點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15815923-%e6%97%a5%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%86%8d%e6%8c%ab-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e6%9a%ab%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be%e5%8d%83%e9%bb%9e-%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e8%b6%85%e9%81%8e3",
