        {
            "title": "中行去年股東應享稅後利潤增長2.18% 末期分派每10股1.169元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國銀行(03988)公布，於2025年度股東應享稅後利潤2430.21億元(人民幣．下同)，按年升2.18%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_03988-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_03988-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會擬派末期現金股利每10股1.169元，連同已派中期現金股利，全年每10股共派2.263元，派息率30%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">去年中行實現營業收入約6599億元，按年升4.28%，其中淨利息收入4407億元，按年減少1.83%，淨息差1.26%亦按年減少0.14個百分點；稅後利潤2579億元，增長2.06%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內減值貸款率與不良貸款率均為1.23%，同樣按年減少0.02個百分點；不良貸款撥備覆蓋率200.37%，按年降0.23個百分點。資本充足率18.85%，則按年升0.09個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15813173-%e4%b8%ad%e8%a1%8c%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e6%87%89%e4%ba%ab%e7%a8%85%e5%be%8c%e5%88%a9%e6%bd%a4%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b72-18-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e5%88%86%e6%b4%be%e6%af%8f10%e8%82%a11-169",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135530_source-web_%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%AD%E8%A1%8C03988-8-%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_source-web_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 17:19:58",
